1
00:00:00,880 --> 00:00:01,600
[SPEAKER_01] Jasno je što čujemo.

2
00:00:02,240 --> 00:00:05,280
[SPEAKER_01] Čujemo se, ali se ne vidimo, kruno.

3
00:00:06,879 --> 00:00:07,759
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje su kruno?

4
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:11,039
